# Local configuration (real Supabase credentials) — see config.example.js
# for the template. Left un-ignored here because this project deploys to
# a static host (Vercel) with no build step, so config.js must ship with
# the repo. The anon key is meant to be public — RLS protects the data,
# not this file. If you'd rather generate it at deploy time instead, see
# DOCUMENTATION.md's "Deploying to Vercel" note and re-add this line.
